      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 66-71.</p><p>Greater Metamagic Master</p><p>Also at 23rd level, when you use your Greater Metamagic, you can use up to 2 Greater Metamagic options on the same spell. In addition, when you cast a 10th-level spell, you can use one Greater Metamagic option that costs 1 Legendary Point for free on that spell.</p></div>",
